{"tid":1792723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"譚耀宗：民生問題加政治煽動致今日局面　王振民：立23條勢在必行","createTime":"2019-12-22T00:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T00:50:35.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fed42e65a86f99a47c10263859d1a33b3edcbcbf","tid":1792723,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3740570/org/2c5cfdcf233829e05e1f84b73c6e6b08.jpg/zKiyshRFQnvp9ryXavC3vSK2Kct3oim3mJinZpiYp2Y?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3740570%2Forg%2F2c5cfdcf233829e05e1f84b73c6e6b08.jpg%2FzKiyshRFQnvp9ryXavC3vSK2Kct3oim3mJinZpiYp2Y%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=3543c8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會委員譚耀宗今日（21日）出席《環球時報》年會時指，香港面對的是民生和立法問題。香港回歸後出現不同的民生問題，住屋、工資的問題未有解決，加上現時外國勢力或明或暗都有動作，有人在政治層面上煽動，演變成深層次矛盾，引致香港現時的風波。<br />\n<br />\n民生問題未解決 演變成深層次矛盾<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗指，香港回歸後，文化和工作制度都與內地不同，都需要時間互相適應，而且民生的問題未有解決，就變成了深層次的矛盾，「有人說是房屋的問題，有些人說是青年人沒有向上流動的渠道，大學生工資跟10多年前差不多。深層次的矛盾再加上政治層面的煽動，就發生了現在當前問題。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/11820/org/d5f5322285542f5d7a041bc09df42a90.jpeg/-qpNuJs9XzheGBcQ2WwLdllJfwKxsp7c-b0EjNO9BIw?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F11820%2Forg%2Fd5f5322285542f5d7a041bc09df42a90.jpeg%2F-qpNuJs9XzheGBcQ2WwLdllJfwKxsp7c-b0EjNO9BIw%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=28ce614a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立23條勢在必行 保障國家安全<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗亦指，普選及基本法23條立法這兩個重要問題，由起草基本法到現在都未能妥善解決，一直爭論到今天，他認為香港近半年的風波都與這兩個問題有關係。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部前部長、清華大學法學院教授王振民表示，香港就《基本法》23條立法是勢在必行。他認為，香港有一股勢力，本質上不願意承認香港已永久回歸祖國事實，並故意抹黑祖國，令國家安全問題上出了問題，導致長時間「暴亂」，因此必須立23條保障國家安全，並強烈呼籲特區政府承擔責任去立法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3741590/org/afb48b4446159023a32ff62a0da8ed58.jpg/0kZeV5Oqz0GObx2tep6b4dwtIJ-FmQMvTLmfvEy5n7w?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3741590%2Forg%2Fafb48b4446159023a32ff62a0da8ed58.jpg%2F0kZeV5Oqz0GObx2tep6b4dwtIJ-FmQMvTLmfvEy5n7w%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=6419a9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君堯​：香港問題本質是「顏色革命」、「貨幣戰爭」<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯在年會上發言稱，香港問題的本質就是「顏色革命」、「貨幣戰爭」。何君堯表示，面對香港的局面，他非常心痛，一直在想問題出在哪兒？他認為，香港的問題不僅僅是政治和經濟的問題，「香港資源不多，地方不大，有的都是人才，但正如美心集團伍淑清女士所言，20多年來，我們失去了兩代人。」他建議，在學校裏要積極引導同學有國家觀念，抵禦外部勢力。"},{"pid":"cf05827e8259bec70b4cb5e1cfe7a6d897301820","tid":1792723,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:23:49.000Z","msg":"香港的問題，咪因為有佢呢班賣港賊..."},{"pid":"b45e21c6dc36a8886d0693414f51323c52c14962","tid":1792723,"uid":197640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:27:12.000Z","msg":"叫大聲啲，遲下美帝真制裁，呢班契弟實喊撚晒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2052fa97629c27e9d89015e2de85f4399f00d8b7","tid":1792723,"uid":277888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"火水救火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245d1f545f4389d0bd6c0f716ba717bfbb1bf6e2","tid":1792723,"uid":335783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:31:36.000Z","msg":"咪佢地搞成咁曪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7846718826cd6109f9fa50d3df22d36e22b4705c","tid":1792723,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45e21c6dc36a8886d0693414f51323c52c14962","tid":1792723,"uid":197640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:27:12.000Z","msg":"叫大聲啲，遲下美帝真制裁，呢班契弟實喊撚晒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa040f35536f28a02e705b8f69d92f4c97e169b","tid":1792723,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:47:00.000Z","msg":"你立完23條，全香港暴動"},{"pid":"076002a78f3e3dbd8070190b7607406ec2a9f6f8","tid":1792723,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨4年之後仲係到先講"},{"pid":"03b32ec90663d435c3f3befef3ebda8f2ca65d6d","tid":1792723,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:50:35.000Z","msg":"總之我就無錯 一定係人地搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}